{"tid":2512473,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[NS] Monster Hunter Rise (60) 瘋狂徹甲輕弩會破壞遊戲體驗","createTime":"2021-05-01T17:47:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T19:42:27.000Z","uid":43016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"411a0a3cd0ff70ab4c6feaf11e567fbfcaf00186","tid":2512473,"uid":43016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T17:47:07.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EiH0xW3VkAYbnxc?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEiH0xW3VkAYbnxc%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=ffa537e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</p><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><a href=\"https://mhrise.wiki-db.com/sim/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmhrise.wiki-db.com%2Fsim%2F&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNobCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=4ba35353\" target=\"_blank\">https://mhrise.wiki-db.com/sim/</a><br />\n<strong>MHR混裝器</strong></p><br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<span class=\"red\">5月尾3.0更新</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3月26日(五)發售<br />\nAlso available on PC(Steam 2022)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官方網站<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.monsterhunter.com/rise/hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.monsterhunter.com%2Frise%2Fhk%2F&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNobCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=c15339af\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.monsterhunter.com/rise/hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">Q&amp;A </span></span><br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\nQ: 唔同版本有咩分別？可唔可以連機？<br />\nA: 日版 港版有中文 美版冇中文<br />\nSwitch MHR冇分ser 全版本可以連機 (需要Nintendo Switch Online)<br />\n<br />\nQ: 新手用咩武器好？<br />\nA: 14種武器各有長短 試下打村任熟習下<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點拎特典？<br />\nA: 火芽左邊隻貓郵差&gt;新增內容<br />\n<br />\nQ : 點係地圖閃燈俾隊友睇<br />\nA : 係場地入邊禁住-號放大地圖，再禁-號<br />\n<br />\nQ : 殺完大怪之後動畫點Skip ?<br />\nA : 兩下B制<br />\n<br />\nQ : 隨從廣場點先開放?<br />\nA : 要行一次先會開到，係火芽面向個位直行到橋尾<br />\n<br />\nQ : 神火卷點拎？<br />\nA : 村5星後玩村任 村長有機會派<br />\n<br />\nQ : 海境S點出？<br />\nA : 玩交易船<br />\n<br />\nQ : 打完boss好似未完咁？<br />\nA : 要等更新(5月尾)！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ : 貓其實有咩技最好<br />\nA : 兩個技必要<br />\n- 強化咆哮 +30%會心<br />\n- cooldown時間一分鐘, 成鋪大部份時間都會發動緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 強化太鼓 x1.05倍攻, x1.2倍防<br />\n- cooldown時間90秒<br />\n<br />\nTips:<br />\n1. 有咩睇咗獵人筆記/心得先<br />\n<br />\n2. 連機嫌眼花可以熄特效<br />\n<br />\n3. 隨從廣場有棵樹可以爬上去 每次完任都有嘢可以執<br />\n（**可以儲一陣先執 唔洗每次去攞）<br />\n<br />\n4. 撳實L1左下角個小地圖可以睇到詳細地圖示記咗嘅嘢 搵礦有小小用<br />\n<br />\n5. 礦有唔少都喺啲勁高嘅地方 要用翔蟲飛嚟飛去 可以配合L1地圖去搵<br />\n<br />\n6. 船艇牡蠣 : 寒冷群島搵 / 狐火鬼燈 : 大社遺跡搵<br />\n<br />\n7. 村任2★ 上 3★要去一去隨從廣場(村右邊過橋)同寵物店老闆吹水<br />\n<br />\n8.村任打完5星 會有個特別許可任務<br />\n連續狩獵打完火龍雷狼同泥翁就可以直接打集會個hr4既首領青熊獸百龍夜行，打完直上hr4<br />\n<br />\n9. 集會所任務出發前記得食團子(即係上幾代既貓飯)<br />\n<br />\n10 : 入左場地之後，-號可以進入地圖，,再L及R睇到好多資訊<br />\n<br />\n11: 下位唔駛諗砌裝，堆高個防就夠<br />\n<br />\n12: ZL+ZR可以直接向瞄準既地方飛<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n開潛艇（新農場）教學：<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=5786&amp;snA=159411\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D5786%26snA%3D159411&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNobCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=40acca9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=5786&amp;snA=159411</a><br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------"},{"pid":"40925ef6f7fb34e93a81241a41e9085a46a45cd8","tid":2512473,"uid":148449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T17:48:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />徹甲滅族團"},{"pid":"ee76d52bbfdbc6e0a825da81e7b83cb0e203a23f","tid":2512473,"uid":43016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T17:49:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVW5s3LssjUu9cnMwFHf1oc2E